        " قَالَ لَنَا أَبُو عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «سِيرُوا وَ اِنْسَلُّوا فَإِنَّهُ أَخَفُّ عَلَيْكُمْ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2501 - Munthir ibn Ja‘far narrated from Yahya ibn Talhah al-Nahdi, who said that Imam Abu Abdullah (as) said to us:\n\"Travel in small groups and slip away quietly; it will be easier for you.\""
        ]
